column20: YES  This vehicle has been considerably upgraded in the last 12 months including- new Mohair Hood refurbished leather seats full sound proofing new fuel tank electronic ignition and cooling fan. The car was fully restored some years ago by a previous owner including the chrome bumper conversion. I believe the milometer was returned to zero at that time. It is registered as a Historic Vehicle and is tax and MOT exempt however I have it MOTd for piece of mind.
